<paragraph id="8BE33697FFBEEB7554C5FF25B58E38D9" blockId="7.[151,1435,151,327]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
<emphasis id="B928EA85FFBEEB7554C5FF25B51D38BF" bold="true" box="[198,355,151,177]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
Habitat 
<typeStatus id="54E78835FFBEEB75552DFF25B51D38BF" box="[302,355,151,177]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">type</typeStatus>
</emphasis>
: Although it seems to have a preference for mountain habitats, this can only be conjectured due to the lack of collections.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE33697FFBEEB7554C5FF50B07D3949" blockId="7.[151,1435,151,327]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
<emphasis id="B928EA85FFBEEB7554C5FF50B53638F2" bold="true" box="[198,328,226,252]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Phenology</emphasis>
: 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCD4B66FFBEEB75555AFF50B66338F2" author="Machado, A. de" box="[345,541,226,252]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="1 - 60" refId="ref44610" refString="Machado, A. de B. (1941) Araignees nouvelles pour la faune portugaise (II) Memorias e Estudos do Museu Zoologico da Universidade de Coimbra, 117, i - xvi, 1 - 60." type="journal article" year="1941">Machado (1941)</bibRefCitation>
collected a male in January and the present data mention females collected in April. 
<taxonomicName id="4C5C4D14FFBEEB75550BFEBAB64F392F" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1884" box="[264,561,264,289]" class="Arachnida" family="Linyphiidae" genus="Bolyphantes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigropictus">
<emphasis id="B928EA85FFBEEB75550BFEBAB64F392F" box="[264,561,264,289]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Bolyphantes nigropictus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a winter species, as in 
<collectingCountry id="F34B7607FFBEEB75576CFEBAB7B3392C" box="[879,973,264,290]" name="Algeria" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Algeria</collectingCountry>
, where adult males were caught from November to April, and females from February to April (
<bibRefCitation id="EFCD4B66FFBEEB755736FE9FB7883949" author="Bosmans, R." box="[821,1014,301,327]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="125 - 161" refId="ref42475" refString="Bosmans, R. (2006 a) Contribution to the knowledge of the Linyphiidae of the Maghreb. Part XI. Miscellaneous Linyphiid genera and additions (Araneae: Linyphiidae: Linyphiinae). Bulletin de la Societe Royal Belge d'Entomologie, 141, 125 - 161." type="journal article" year="2006">Bosmans 2006a</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
